                        <h1>December 16, 2009</h1>                                  
                        Mobile digital TV reception is becoming a reality in 2010, and you can see it firsthand at CES, January 7-10, in Las Vegas, Nevada. Read about this and other emerging technologies in this edition of CES Up to the Minute, and get ready for the world’s largest consumer technology tradeshow.

